body.name: Humty Dumty Remote Control Fighter Jet Airplane, 2.4 Ghz Aircraft Gyro Stabilization System, Gravity Sensing, Stunt Roll Aerobatic. RC Gift for Kids, Teens, Adults, Boys.
features: High Quality EPP Material: Crafted from high-quality EPP lightweight flexible material, this RC plane is specially designed for model aircraft, providing superior flexibility and impact resistance. With a flight weight of around 24g, it can withstand multiple impacts. The upgraded landing gear enhances stability and facilitates easier taxiing takeoff.

Powerful Performance: Experience exceptional performance with the high-speed hollow cup motor, offering fast speed, low energy consumption, and a long service life. The built-in 3-axis gyroscope flight self-stabilization system ensures intelligent balance, making flight easier. The rear push dual engine power provides enhanced strength.

2.4 GHz Remote Control: Utilize the standard 2.4 GHz remote control system, providing a strong and stable signal with a remote control distance greater than 100m. Enjoy long-lasting power and a smooth flight experience. Even novices can quickly get started, operate easily, and fly effortlessly.

Long Flight Time: Equipped with 3.7v 150mAh rechargeable lithium batteries, this RC plane offers an extended playing time of more than 15 minutes. The battery charging time is approximately 40 minutes, ensuring more time in the air.

Included Accessories: The package includes the SU-35 RC plane, a remote controller, front landing gear, rear landing gear, 3.7v 150mAh Lipo batteries, a USB charging cable, two spare propellers. Note: To prevent propeller damage during landing, close the throttle before landing and let the aircraft glide with the wind for a smooth landing.
body.description: Embark on thrilling airborne adventures with the Su-35 Remote Control Fighter Jet, a high-performance aircraft that promises excitement for pilots of all ages. Boasting advanced 2.4 GHz technology, this sleek jet ensures seamless and interference-free communication, allowing for a superior flying experience. The integrated gyro stabilization system adds an extra layer of control, making aerobatic maneuvers and smooth flights effortlessly accessible to pilots, whether they are kids, teens, or adults. With gravity sensing technology, intuitive control takes center stage, elevating the flying experience to new heights. Impress onlookers with dazzling aerial displays using the Su-35's stunt roll aerobatic capabilities. This RC Fighter Jet isn't just about performance—it's also a perfect gift for aviation enthusiasts and anyone who appreciates the excitement of flying. Built with durability in mind, the Su-35 features a robust construction that can withstand the rigors of flight, ensuring long-lasting enjoyment for pilots of all skill levels. The inclusion of captivating lights and sounds adds a realistic touch to the experience, enhancing the overall immersion in the world of aviation. Unleash your imagination and command the skies with the Su-35 Remote Control Fighter Jet, a sleek and powerful aircraft that promises hours of airborne delight.
